name: The King was Killed on the Halloween Party
description: The Mutant come to the king during the Halloween party disguised in a chicken costume. He participated in the party, when the king was about to rest, the mutant sprang into action and finally a fierce battle ensued. Because the king was tired and there was no prior preparation. finally the king Indukayam was killed on the night of the halloween party. This is really not a nightmare but a terrible reality for the people he loves. that's how life, Bad and good always take turns filling the void of themes on this earth.
